\v 5 Q Danidzira kwazvo, usarega, da mdzira nezwi rako sehwamanda,
\s uparidzire vanhu vangu kudarika kwavo,
\p neimba yaJakobho zvivi zvavo.
\v 2 Kunya
\s nge zvakadaro, vanonditsvaka zuva ri
\s mwe nerimwe, vachifarira kuziva nzira
\s dzangu; vanokumbira kwandiri mirayiro
\s yakarurama, sorudzi runoita zvakaru
