\s kwauri, pfuma yamarudzi avanhu ichauya kwauri.
\p
\v 6 Ngamera zhinji-zhinji dzichakufukidza, nemhuru dzengamera eMidhiani neEfa; vose veShebha vachauya, vachauya nendarama nezvinonhuwira, vachaparidza kurumbidzwa kwaJehovha.
\p
\v 7 Mapoka ose amakwai eKedhari achaunganidzirwa kwauri, makondobwe eNebhayoti achakushumira; zvichaiswa paaritari yangu ndichizvifarira, ndichashongedza imba yokukudzwa kwangu.
\v 8 Ndianiko ava vanobhururuka segore, senjiva dzinouya kumawindo ezvirugu zvadzo?
\p
\v 9 Zvirokwazvo, zvivi zvichandimirira, nezvikepe zveTarishishi zvichatungamira zvichiuya navanakomana vako vanobva kure, vachiuya nesirivha yavo nendarama yavo kuzviisa kuzita raJehovha Mwari wako, nokunoMutsvene waIsiraeri, nokuti ndiye wakakushongedza.
\v 10 Vatorwa vachavaka masvingo ako, madzimambo avo achakushumira; nokuti ndakakurova nokutsamwa kwangu, asi ndakakunzwira nyasha nengoni dzangu.
\v 11 Masuo ako achagara akazaruka nguva dzose, haangazarirwi masikati nousiku, kuti vauyise kwauri pfuma yamarudzi avanhu namadzimambo avo, akatapwa.
\p
\v 12 Nokuti rudzi noushe, zvinoramba kukushumira, zvichaparara; zvirokwazvo marudzi iwayo achaparadzwa chose.
\v 13 Zvinobwinya zveRebhanoni zvichauya kwauri, misaipuresi, nemipaini nemifiri pamwechete, kuti ndishongedze nzvimbo yeimba yangu tsvene; uye ndichabwinyisa nzvimbo yetsoka dzangu.
\v 14 Vanakomana vavatambudzi vako vachauya kwauri vachikotama; vose vaikuzvidza vachazvikotamisa pasi-pasi petsoka dzako; vachakutumidza zita rokuti, "Guta raJehovha, Zioni roMutsvene waIsiraeri."
\v 15 Wakanga wakasiyiwa nokuvengwa, kusisina munhu aipfuura nomukati mako, asi zvino ndichakuita chinhu chinorumbidzwa nokusingaperi, chinofarirwa kusvikira kumarudzi mazhinji.
\v 16 Uchamwawo mukaka wamarudzi, uchamwa mazamu amadzimambo; ipapo uchaziva kuti ini iettoYtta, tidttit W.WO
\p nesi wako, noMudzikinuri wako, waMasimbaose waJakobho.
\v 1
\v 7 Panzvimbo yendarira ndichauya nendarama, panzvimbo yedare ndichauya nesirivha, panzvimbo yamatanda safuri, napanzvi
\s mbo yamabwe dare. Rugare ndicharugadza ruve madzishe ako, noKururama kuve vabati vako.
\p
\v 18 Zvinoitwa nesimba hazvichazonzwiki panyika pamiganho yako; asi uchatumidza masvingo ako zita rokuti, "Ruponeso, namasuo ako Rumbidzo."
\p
\v 19 Zuva harichazovi chiedza chako masikati, mwedzi haungazokuvhenekeri nokupenya kwawo; asi Jehovha achava kwauri chiedza chisingaperi, naMwari wako kunaka kwako.
\v 20 Zuva rako harichazoviri, mwedzi wako haungatapudziki; nokuti Jehovha achava chiedza chako chisingaperi, mazuva okuchema kwako achaguma.
\p
\v 21 Vanhu vako vose vachava vakarurama, vachagara nhaka yenyika nokusingaperi, vachava davi randakasima, nebasa ramaoko angu, kuti ndikudzwe.
\v 2
\v 2 Muduku achava chiuru, akadukupa achava rudzi rune simba; ini Jehovha ndichakurumidza kuzviita nenguva yazvo.
